OL,5, The government is facing a High Court  
OL,6, challenge over its use of WhatsApp and 
OL,7, instant messaging.                     
OL,9,FOfficial guidelines have emerged which 
OL,10,Fsay ministers must ensure instant      
OL,11,Fmessages on an internal system are     
OL,12,Fdeleted.                               
OL,14,FTransparency campaigners say this is   
OL,15,F"unlawful" and have secured a judicial 
OL,16,Freview of the rules.                   
OL,18,FMinisters are banned from using        
OL,19,FWhatsApp and private email for         
OL,20,Fdiscussing government business.        
